goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:1690:Drafts for approval, per-conversation prep sheets (their background, why-them, the 10 questions), call debriefs recorded against `pipeline.json` cards, and niche-hypothesis updates flagged for `NICHE.md`.
