goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:2313:Referrals and weak ties carry most opportunity; portals carry volume. This command runs the human layer: the listening tour, informational interviews, referral asks, cold outreach, and follow-up cadence. Nothing sends without the user's approval of the final text.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:2335:- After a conversation: thank-you within 24–72 hours, send anything promised, report back outcomes later ("took your advice, here's what happened" — the most underused relationship builder).
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:2340:3–5 conversations/week during active search; 10–25 outreach messages/week depending on urgency; 2–3 follow-up blocks/week. Watch response rate: under ~15% on warmish outreach means the message or the targeting is off — diagnose in `review` before sending more.
