goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:3156:+  Schema: `{version, updated_at, cards:[{id,target_id?,lead_id?,role,stage,warmth,last_touch_at?,next_action?,due_at?,owner,status,reason_code?,thread_ids:[],artifact_ids:[],approval_ids:[],proof_ids:[]}]}`.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:3157:+- `leads.json`: posting leads found by `scout`, including the bench.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:3159:+- `sources.json`: boards, newsletters, communities, saved searches, and job channels.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:3161:+- `targets.json`: employer/segment target list and Top 10.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:3163:+- `capabilities.json`: setup results and best available execution rungs.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:3165:+- `metrics.json`: quotas, weekly funnel metrics, and the mutable evidence inbox index.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:3166:+  Schema: `{version, updated_at, quotas:{weekly_applications}, weeks:[{week_start,outreach_sent,applications,screens,interviews,offers,response_rate?,notes?}], evidence_inbox:[{id,event_id,source,profile_sections:[],claim,status,created_at,drained_at?}]}`.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:3167:+- `approvals.jsonl`: append-only agent-written approval records, one JSON object per line.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:3169:+- `events.jsonl`: append-only server-written request events, one JSON object per line.
