goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:7501:+The agent validates the current artifact hash before appending an approval record. Hash mismatch means re-present the item.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:7505:+`await --ids ... --timeout N` is a blocking CLI bridge used by the agent. It tails `events.jsonl` from `goodwork/.await-cursor`, waits for matching item IDs or event IDs, and exits when all requested events arrive, a rejection arrives, or timeout expires.
