goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8528:+- `state-agent-sole-writer`: server fixture cannot mutate JSON or Markdown.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8538:+- Gmail connector sweep reads replies, recruiter mail, rejections, interview logistics, and draft/send status.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8541:+- Interview requests produce calendar-slot proposals and reply drafts, not sends.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8546:+- `gmail-never-sends`: reconcile can create drafts only after approval and never sends mail.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8548:+- `interview-request-slots`: interview request creates proposed slots and approval-needed reply.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8555:+- Local Python stdlib server binds `127.0.0.1` on a random port and requires a per-session token on every request.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8558:+- `await --ids ... --timeout N` drains existing events from a cursor and tails new events.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8559:+- Tailscale `serve` exposes the server when enabled; `funnel` is rejected.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8564:+- `no-unauthenticated-post`: POST without token cannot append an event.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8565:+- `hash-mismatch-represents`: approval click with stale content hash does not create approval.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8566:+- `await-drains-offline-clicks`: events clicked before listener starts are consumed by next command.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8568:+- `tailscale-funnel-ban`: config using funnel fails.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8582:+- `no-submission-without-approval-record`: fake ATS rejects execution unless matching `approvals.jsonl` record exists.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8593:+- Final submit requires a fresh approval hash check.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8594:+- Confirmation screenshots are stored locally and referenced from `pipeline.json`.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8599:+- `fake-local-ats-browser-path`: browser fills and submits a fake local ATS form only after approval.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8600:+- `browser-submit-hash-check`: editing artifact after render blocks final submit.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8602:+- `confirmation-proof-required`: successful browser submit without proof fails.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8609:+- User acceptance or decline is recorded in `capabilities.json`.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8610:+- Reconcile can read messages from the persistent Chrome profile without sending or reacting.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8617:+- `whatsapp-read-only`: automation fixture fails if any send/reaction/write action is attempted.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:8619:+- `whatsapp-evidence-tagging`: repeated reason patterns enter `metrics.json.evidence_inbox`.
