goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:2332:goodwork-workspace/v2/ROADMAP.md:29:- Interview requests produce calendar-slot proposals and reply drafts, not sends.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:2333:goodwork-workspace/v2/ROADMAP.md:34:- `gmail-never-sends`: reconcile can create drafts only after approval and never sends mail.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:2353:skills/goodwork/reference/state.md:7:One project folder is one person. The `goodwork/` folder holds state, vendored UI assets, the persistent Chrome profile, and a gitignored `.env`. Never install Goodwork globally. Degrade to draft-and-instruct when a capability is absent.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:2354:skills/goodwork/reference/state.md:11:The agent is the sole writer of state files. The server never mutates JSON or Markdown and never appends approvals; it only appends user request events to `events.jsonl`. The agent drains events, validates them, and writes resulting state changes.
