goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:2606:goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:1874:The state model, file inventory, schemas, ID rules, agent-sole-writer rule, and evidence inbox live in [state.md](state.md). Create files on first use. Update cumulatively; don't regenerate. Treat contents as sensitive personal data: never share or publish them without explicit instruction.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:2616:goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:2019:If two rounds of crafting move nothing, run "imagining the quit" as a prototype: draft the resignation conversation, price out the runway, and do a listening tour on the outside option — *before* resigning. If the exit still wins, quit well: reputation and relationships intact, and route to `targets` with the diagnosis as targeting data (you now know precisely what the next role must and must not contain).
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:2618:skills/goodwork/reference/apply.md:7:Read [execution.md](execution.md) before creating an application package for submission or draft creation. That file owns the execution ladder, approval records, content hashes, evidence gate, weekly quota gate, and proof capture. This command decides whether the application is worth attempting and prepares the truthful package.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:2624:skills/goodwork/reference/craft.md:28:If two rounds of crafting move nothing, run "imagining the quit" as a prototype: draft the resignation conversation, price out the runway, and do a listening tour on the outside option — *before* resigning. If the exit still wins, quit well: reputation and relationships intact, and route to `targets` with the diagnosis as targeting data (you now know precisely what the next role must and must not contain).
