goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:3204:goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:4323:+Operational state is JSON/JSONL; narrative state stays Markdown. The agent is the sole state writer, with the local server limited to appending request events. Outbound work uses the execution ladder and hard gates in `reference/execution.md`.
