goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:3210:goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:4399:+6. **State touch**: when a command reads or writes operational JSON/JSONL, load [reference/state.md](reference/state.md). When it creates, sends, submits, drafts, or automates, load [reference/execution.md](reference/execution.md).
