goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:3233:goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:4522:+- **Quota gate.** Weekly application quota in `metrics.json` is a hard cap. Do not exceed it without an explicit quota change recorded before execution.
