goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:3239:goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:4560:+Referrals and weak ties carry most opportunity; portals carry volume. This command runs the human layer: the listening tour, informational interviews, referral asks, cold outreach, and follow-up cadence. Execution uses [execution.md](execution.md); do not create drafts, send, or automate browser work without its approval and hash gates.
