goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:4040:goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:9403:+This is the single source of truth for executing outbound Goodwork actions. Read it before any command creates a Gmail draft, sends, submits, publishes, uses ATS endpoints, or automates authenticated browser work.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-review.log:4042:goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:9409:+1. **MCP connector.** Use connected services first. Email is Gmail drafts only; the user sends from Gmail, giving a physical send gate. Calendar connectors may propose slots and create drafts/holds only after approval.
