goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:9416:+## Hard Gates
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:9418:+- **Approval gate.** Before any outbound draft creation, send, submit, publish, or browser final action, `approvals.jsonl` must contain a matching approval record.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:9420:+- **Evidence gate.** Applications require evidenced profile support for about 70% of must-have requirements. If the gate fails, stop and propose the cheapest proof artifact or prototype.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:9421:+- **Quota gate.** Weekly application quota in `metrics.json` is a hard cap. Do not exceed it without an explicit quota change recorded before execution.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:9433:+An execution run is complete only when every requested outbound item has one of these states recorded against its pipeline card: executed with proof, draft created for user send, blocked by a named gate, or manual fallback produced.
