goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:12213:-An updated `PIPELINE.md`, today's due actions pushed to `daily`, and any diagnosis with its routing (which command fixes the constriction).
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:12259:+1. Gmail via connector: replies, recruiter mail, interview logistics, rejection notices, and sent/draft status where available.
goodwork-workspace/v2/codex-spec.log:12279:+Updated `pipeline.json`, drafted replies or calendar proposals awaiting approval, unmatched inbound items needing user judgment, and today's changed priorities for `daily`.
